Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:03:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Promise from a Distant Day!\NThe Pirates' Song and a Small Whale!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we should leave Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take someone we can't find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Where in the world did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew! Okay, you can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift your invisibility power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was terrified we'd get \Ncaught the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did find out what brought\NTyrant Kuma to Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, Absalom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tyrant Kuma came to tell us the name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the successor to the\Nformer Warlord, Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His successor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that's not the important part.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The successor is a man called Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.12,0:04:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pulled a truly nasty stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist Ace, 2nd Division Commander\Nof the Whitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been imprisoned in Impel Down"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's well known that Ace is\None of Whitebeard's top dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government just got\Ntheir hands on a powerful card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how they play it,\Nthis could completely change the Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a serious situation on our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time for Moria-sama\Nto be dead to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see where you're coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm more interested... in finding a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Bring me a corpse that turns you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna marry a living woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:38.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Day After Defeating Moria"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.90,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone slept all day in that courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure. We were up all the\Nprevious night fighting like mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibble on some cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese doesn't cut it!\NCheese doesn't energize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start hauling the ingredients\NI need to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the members of the Victim\NAssociation don't want to budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're eating over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is just so happy to see\Nthe sun for the first time in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are crying tears \Nof joy while sunbathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did all of that energy come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so weird! It's a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a mountain of additional food
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Non top of everything that was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who did that. There are\Nsome nice people out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they even loaded your ship\Nwith all of this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even assuming it was Christmas,\Nthis is far too generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.56,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a glass armband!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I claim this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you know what'll happen\Nif you take any of the treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can have it! There aren't any gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that how this works? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have a single\Npiece of treasure for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't take treasure from\Nthe people who saved us, Namizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! This is out. \NIt's studded with gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It popped right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Namizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is rather strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some odd reason, I don't feel\Nlike this is the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, are you Lola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Did I tell you my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lola...? Wh-Whoa, wait! Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boar zombie was her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be confused, huh? \NI'll fill you in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, take this. It's \Nmy way of thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure? You're thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami gave away some of our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead. Is this everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A storm? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light is seeping into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you told us, we would have carried it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe shouldn't let our savior work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Zoro up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs absolute rest, \Nso he's in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought the stuff you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Zoro so badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He nearly lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think something must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while we were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I sincerely doubt \Nthat man simply left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's strange how Luffy\Nis bursting with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's up with that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I saw what went down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what happened from beginning to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill you in on what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold up!\N--Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.19,0:09:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why?! You were pretty cool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were like, "Instead of the\Nswordsman's life, take mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.61,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now start talking. What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what happened\Nafter I blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Warlord had yet \Nanother shocking ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pressed his paw against Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It repelled all of the "damage"\Nthat Straw Hat had taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.61,0:10:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His damage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a bubble of agony. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to take his place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take all of his pain and \Nsuffering unto yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be impossible for you to survive\Nwhen you are already on the brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.16,0:10:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a small taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the swordsman started\Nscreaming bloody murder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he touched a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but I \Nthought he was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes it so touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seriously made me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That explains why Luffy is\Ndoing well while Zoro is bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did all of this blood come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.39,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's tell everyone\Nabout the Straw Hats' heroic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm itching to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't risk his life out of\Na desire to earn our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if they learned that\NLuffy's pain hurt a friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how badly are you \Ndying to tell everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that everyone is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their captain is so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you acting like you knew\Nwhat happened? What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask such an insensitive question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that everyone is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wanna tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keep that manly heroic story to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delish! I've never eaten \Nsuch good food before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here! Try this! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's been years since\Nwe've eaten a decent meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked up a storm! \NDon't let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I get to eat your cooking again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is lip-smacking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That skeleton is hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.55,0:13:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly--oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After eating until I was full\Nboth yesterday and today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have gained weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though I'm a skeleton!"\NI can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, you rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come that skeleton is able to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's a hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a clever skeleton, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.08,0:13:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you able to move around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it doesn't really matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, dinner!\N--Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Oh, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have a toast\Nand it still turned into a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping right through all this noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here he's the toughest guy in the crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--This is for Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now drink away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! This will fix Zoro\Nright up, since it's his favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of treatment is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work? Then how about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. I'll gladly accept\Nyour sentiment alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only your sentiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a piano in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I thought you only played the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can play most instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd like to touch on \Nan earlier conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I also saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was greatly moved by what you two did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful to have comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't include me in that.\NI merely made a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you bore the same resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to pick a song?\NI'll take a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? I can request anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, didn't you just ask for a request?!\N--♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail leisurely with the sea breeze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail with the waves ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The setting sun romps about\Non the other side of the tide ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A ring of birds in the sky sing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Bid farewell to the port\Nof the weaving village ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ As we set sail, we \Nshall sing heartily ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Silver and gold waves \Nturn into ocean spray ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We are off, bound for \Nthe ends of the ocean ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bink's Booze." I thought\NI recognized the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee! Yahoo! Keep it going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! I know this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks and the guys used to sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A long time ago,\Nall of the pirates would sing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sang it in good times and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna join our crew now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've got your shadow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hit the seas without\Nfear of the sun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that. There was one thing\NI neglected to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised one of my comrades something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must tend to that first \Nor I will lose face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're talking \Nabout Laboon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about it. \NFranky and Robin told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.29,0:18:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the name of the whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is at a certain cape--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Brook! We met Laboon\Nat Twin Cape. Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew that Laboon
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had been waiting there for his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to return for the past fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, what's wrong?\NThe tempo is getting slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the symbol of\Nour promise to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we come back, don't remove that\Nmark by hitting your head. Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.60,0:19:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, whale! I'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:20:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, was I ever surprised when I learned\Nthat you're the surviving member
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the band of pirates he's been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still remember your promise to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Laboon would be thrilled if he knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked! This is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true? Did you actually meet Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though fifty years have passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon is still waiting for us at that cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also bore witness.\NWe saw him with our own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was as big as a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:21:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we left him, the cutie \Nwas about the size of a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a stubborn streak, but he loved music.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...picture him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never been this happy in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:22:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that whale come from?\NIt's following our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have gotten separated from its pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor thing. The ocean is a big place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks sad. Well, it's still just a calf.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yorkie, why don't we play a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea, Brook! Hey, everyone!\NGrab your instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show him what the \NRumbar Pirates that make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,crying children laugh are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, you are our dear comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can't take you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line is so dangerous,\Nwe want you to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will swing around the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear we will come back\Nto this cape to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.51,0:23:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook's Past! A Sad Farewell\Nwith His Cheerful Comrade!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
